  "hooks": {
    "PreCommit": [{
      "matcher": "",
      "hooks": [{ "type": "command", "command": "lna remind-capture" }]
    }]
  }
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Short output (< 200 tokens)
- [ ] Skips if no staged changes
- [ ] Always exits 0 (non-blocking)
- [ ] Clear call-to-action with command/tool reference
